## CHIMATA'S FAIR MARKET
*"Every item has a proper value. Let's find it."*

**Operator:** Chimata Tenkyuu

Players can sell unwanted items here at fair market value. Chimata has a philosophical investment in equitable trade — she will not lowball, and she will not overpay. She knows what things are worth and will tell you.

| Service | Details |
|---|---|
| Sell Items | Standard items sold at 50% market value (PHB rules) |
| Sell Tower Loot | DM-adjudicated value based on rarity and condition |

**Notes:**
- Chimata will refuse to buy stolen goods if she suspects foul play
- Haggling is permitted but she is rarely moved — DC 18 Persuasion to improve rate by 10%
- She keeps a running ledger. She remembers what you sold and when.

