## KOURINDOU ANNEX — Tools & Curiosities
*"I know what it's called. Whether I know what it does is another matter."*

**Operator:** Rinnosuke Morichika, half-youkai antique dealer

Rinnosuke's innate ability lets him identify the name and original purpose of any non-magical item on sight — though practical use sometimes eludes him. Stocks tools, utility equipment, kits, and the occasional inexplicable outside-world object.

**Inventory:** All PHB tools, artisan's tools, gaming sets, and standard kits at listed prices.

| Service | Cost | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| Item Identification (non-magical) | Free | Name and original purpose only |
| Usage Explanation | 50gp | How the item was intended to be used |
| Outside-World Appraisal | Free | He will offer to buy it. He will offer too little. |

**Notes:**
- Isekai'd players are of extreme professional interest to him
- He will absolutely ask about phones, appliances, and modern tools
- Anything he cannot identify goes in a cabinet labeled "PENDING" — there is a lot in that cabinet

