## SANAE'S CURSE REMOVAL — Moriya Method
*"Don't worry! We can definitely handle this. Probably!"*

**Operator:** Sanae Kochiya

Curse removal through Moriya Shrine divine techniques. Same services as Reimu, presented with significantly more enthusiasm and a free pamphlet about the Moriya Shrine.

**Services:** Identical to Reimu's pricing above.

**Moriya Bonus:**
After curse removal, Sanae offers a short divine blessing: **advantage on the next saving throw made within 24 hours** *(once per player per week)*.

**Reimu vs. Sanae:**
